      • onAuthenticationUserConsentRequried

        void onAuthenticationUserConsentRequried(java.lang.String privacyPolicy)
        This callback is invoked when the end-user’s consent to Jumio’s privacy policy is legally required. Please call AuthenticationCustomSDKController.setUserConsented() when the end-user has accepted.
        Parameters:
        privacyPolicy - Jumio privacy policy URL
